name: Face another people
description:
While traveling, I looked into the eyes of people who attracted me with their charisma. In those eyes, as in a mirror of the soul, I saw my reflection. I hope these portraits will allow you to feel a diverse range of deep emotions.
 The collection was created by me in 2015 on a Bronica film camera and has never been posted online. It has over 100 frames.
With each purchase of NFT, I am ready to send the original large-format film photo by mail or at your convenience.
